{"tid":1152710,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利狗柒還柒 鏝迷唔該唔好借機話自己唔係金錢足球","createTime":"2019-05-13T06:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T09:18:46.000Z","uid":191725,"like":55,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c869eaa1fa4ebdb1caf6c03b8cd41a115c06a5","tid":1152710,"uid":191725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"係有錢咪認囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣排到兩隊正選都死撐話廢<br />\n好好地認自己隊波係勁 係陣容厚 我諗冇人會反對<br />\n<br />\n依兩年曼城成績有目共睹 贏盡掌聲<br />\n但鏝迷係要講到自己揸住隊爭4陣容咁<br />\n係要講到成個fairy tale 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實隊波屈 贏冠軍<br />\n同隊波爭崩頭先贏到冠軍<br />\n都會受人尊敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下外國新聞邊有人focus係曼城用咗幾多錢<br />\n個個都讚連續2季拎咁高分依個壯舉<br />\n<br />\n下下話自己個陣唔掂同富二代話自己窮有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec085e32f48e14d3adf3458660eeca6b544088ca","tid":1152710,"uid":4957,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:52:01.000Z","msg":"傻左 睇返上面個po la 阿曼車都駛得多$過利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98854e2aaf36330d508958107b719a2c1b86f08e","tid":1152710,"uid":32247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"利記找個亞冠變咗英超大清洗日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1b9e851ca46d04c450f7bfb5ce4f3aacb86edb","tid":1152710,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:53:22.000Z","msg":"邊個唔認<br />\n邊個講到成個fairy-tail 咁<br />\n想知"},{"pid":"fdf5029ce395da1037aa29f60ed60af813294b29","tid":1152710,"uid":32247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98854e2aaf36330d508958107